---
title: Honey-Glazed Haloumi & Roast Veggie Salad with Garlic Yoghurt & Flaked Almonds
description: Here’s a hearty vegetarian meal that brings inspiration from across the globe to your plate. Flavourful haloumi meets roasted vegetables tossed with Mumbai-style spices, and there’s a tangy yoghurt dressing and toasted almonds to finish it off.

*Keep an eye out...Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
